data.description: Seller offering 2-1 buy down to help with your interest rate!! If your looking for a turn key home in a great neighborhood close to shopping, restaurants and so much more....this is your home! As soon as you walk into this immaculately cared for home, you will notice all the attention to detail and pride of ownership. Featuring a large open concept floor plan, massive kitchen with stainless appliances and quartz countertops, large pantry, indoor laundry room, 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and large cozy living room. The master suite bathroom features double walk in closets, walk in shower, 2 sinks and a spa like feel! The backyard is set up and ready for entertaining with two separate patio areas, a side yard dog run, a small garden space and separate fenced space for all your kids toys, etc! The 2 car garage is actually a 2.5, featuring a small tandem side area for extra storage or work benches. This home also has solar! Come see it before its sold!
